    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You ward an area, preventing it from being easily discovered, magically or otherwise.</em></p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><p>You apply any of the following benefits to the chosen area, affecting either the entrances to the area or the area itself:</p><ul><li>Sound can't pass from outside the warded area to inside, or vice versa.</li><li>Entrances or the edges of the warded area appear shrouded in fog, preventing creatures from seeing in or out.</li><li>The area and everything within it canâ€™t be targeted by any @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.MQixQwPAnbjydC5D.JournalEntryPage.ppulpuqZdX9NWhDW]{divination magic} or perceived through magical scrying. Divination magic will behave as if the area and things within it doesn't exist.</li></ul><p>If you use 0.4 pounds of pure @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.wV3r0XKYOLYdI0nz]{Diamond Dust}, typically valued at 200 gold, while casting this spell, this spell is permanent until dispelled. This consumes the diamond dust.</p><p></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> The size of the cube increases by 50 ft. for each spell level above 4th level.</p></div></div>",
